Package: psychinterpreter
Title: LLM-powered interpretation of factor and cluster analyses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Matthias Kloft [aut, cre, cph] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1845-6957>)
Maintainer: Matthias Kloft <kloft.dev+rctbayespower@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(person("Matthias", "Kloft",
  email = "kloft.dev+psychinterpreter@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1845-6957")))
Description: We provide functions to automate the naming and describing of factors in exploratory factor analysis and clusters in cluster analysis using the large language models (LLMs) via the 'ellmer' package. We further provide S3 methods to interface with commonly used packages, such as 'psych', 'lavaan', and 'mirt'.
